room_title: Escape room "Shanghaied" by Escapology Rockwall in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: The set up, clues, the rooms, are all very elaborate and well put together! The staff was friendly and very accommodating. I will DEF be doing this again!

room_title: Escape room "Shanghaied" by Escapology Rockwall in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We took our 15 year old son along with 6 friends and they had a great time. Highly recommend this place!

room_title: Escape room "Shanghaied" by Escapology Rockwall in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Nice aesthetics to the room. The decor at escapology is always good. Same formula as all of their rooms, mostly locks and puzzles to find codes for locks. Good, solid beginner room, though.
